sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    %% Flow 1: Model Registration via REST API
    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over Client,DB: Flow 1 - Model Registration via REST API
        participant Client as Client<br/>(Dashboard/SDK)
        participant IstioGW as Istio Ingress<br/>Gateway<br/>443/TCP TLS 1.3
        participant MRProxy as model-registry<br/>proxy<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
        participant DB as PostgreSQL/MySQL<br/>5432/3306 TCP

        Client->>IstioGW: HTTPS/443<br/>OAuth2/kubeflow-userid
        IstioGW->>MRProxy: HTTP/8080<br/>Istio mTLS<br/>AuthorizationPolicy
        MRProxy->>DB: SQL (GORM)<br/>Configurable TLS<br/>Username/password
        DB-->>MRProxy: Query results
        MRProxy-->>IstioGW: JSON response
        IstioGW-->>Client: HTTPS response
    end

    %% Flow 2: InferenceService Synchronization
    rect rgb(255, 245, 230)
        Note over K8sAPI,MRProxy: Flow 2 - InferenceService Synchronization
        participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP TLS
        participant MRCtrl as model-registry<br/>controller<br/>8081/TCP

        K8sAPI->>MRCtrl: Watch stream (TLS)<br/>InferenceService events<br/>ServiceAccount token
        MRCtrl->>MRProxy: HTTP/8080<br/>Istio mTLS<br/>Bearer Token
        MRProxy-->>MRCtrl: Model metadata
        MRCtrl->>K8sAPI: HTTPS/443<br/>Patch InferenceService<br/>ServiceAccount token
    end

    %% Flow 3: Model Download via CSI Storage Initializer
    rect rgb(230, 255, 230)
        Note over KServe,Storage: Flow 3 - Model Download via CSI
        participant KServe as KServe Agent
        participant CSI as CSI storage<br/>initializer
        participant Storage as Storage Backend<br/>(S3/GCS)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

        KServe->>CSI: Init container invocation<br/>model-registry:// URI
        CSI->>MRProxy: HTTP/8080<br/>Resolve model artifact URI
        MRProxy-->>CSI: Artifact storage URI
        CSI->>Storage: HTTPS/443<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>Provider-specific auth
        Storage-->>CSI: Model artifacts
        CSI-->>KServe: Model files on volume
    end

    %% Flow 4: Async Model Upload Job
    rect rgb(255, 230, 255)
        Note over AsyncJob,Sigstore: Flow 4 - Async Model Upload Job
        participant AsyncJob as async-upload<br/>job (Python)
        participant SrcStore as Source Storage<br/>(S3/OCI/HF)<br/>443/TCP
        participant DstStore as Dest Storage<br/>(S3/OCI)<br/>443/TCP
        participant Sigstore as Sigstore<br/>(Fulcio/Rekor)<br/>443/TCP

        AsyncJob->>SrcStore: HTTPS/443<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>AWS IAM / Docker auth / API key
        SrcStore-->>AsyncJob: Model files
        AsyncJob->>DstStore: HTTPS/443<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>AWS IAM / Docker auth
        DstStore-->>AsyncJob: Upload confirmation
        AsyncJob->>Sigstore: HTTPS/443<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>OIDC identity token
        Sigstore-->>AsyncJob: Signature/transparency log entry
        AsyncJob->>MRProxy: HTTPS/443<br/>TLS<br/>Bearer Token
        MRProxy-->>AsyncJob: Registration confirmation
    end
